akka.typed.internal

Class FunctionRef<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.typed.ActorRef<T>
      • akka.typed.internal.WatchableRef<T>
        • akka.typed.internal.FunctionRef<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActorRefImpl<T>, java.lang.Comparable<ActorRef<?>>

    public final class FunctionRef<T>
extends WatchableRef<T>
    A local synchronous ActorRef that invokes the given function for every message send. This reference can be watched and will do the right thing when it receives a DeathWatchNotification. This reference cannot watch other references.
